name: JAS 17.4.27.18.28
description:
This painting was created in my Semaphore software which filters a camera input to sample color and value ranges to paint with. This is the only signed painting I ever made with this tool!

It was created for a remote lecture in Jacob Ciocci's digital painting class at Oberlin: https://youtu.be/_5YLPA_3l2I?t=79
